snippet: Rescuers on Monday safely recovered 13 more people from a tourist boat that sank after hitting a reef in central Indonesia but were searching for a Dutch man and an Italian woman who were still missing, officials said.
abstract: Rescuers safely recover 13 more people from tourist boat that sank after hitting reef in central Indonesia but are searching for Dutch man and Italian woman who are still missing.
lead_paragraph: Rescuers on Monday safely recovered 13 more people from a tourist boat that sank after hitting a reef in central Indonesia but were searching for a Dutch man and an Italian woman who were still missing, officials said.

headline.main: Indonesia: Fishermen Save 13 From Tourist Boat That Sank
